modName: Guy Fawkes mask Dragon Priest replacer
summary: A little mod which replace all the dragon priest mask with the one used by Anonymous. For all of those who want to wear it for the civil war in Skyrim ! And I know that we are Legion ! ^^
descriptionHtml:
A little mod which replace all the dragon priest masks by the one used by Anonymous.
For all of those who want to wear it for the civil war in Skyrim ! And I know that we are Legion ! ^^

Installation note : Simply extract the file in your Skyrim Data folder.


If you want a stand alone version you can find it here : http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17151

I made the mask mesh and the textures.

Tell me if you see bugs !


---Please do not use it without my permission, and if you want to make it stand alone before I do, don\'t share it on the nexus, thank you. :) ---



--Thanks to Bethesda for this great game and for all the modders writing tutorial for Skyrim on the internet.
author: MoicoM
